# Misc
*.tsbuildinfo

# Defensive: catch emitted `.js` / `.d.ts` files that leak into a
# package's `src/` when someone runs a bare `tsc` instead of `tsc -b`
# (the proper composite-aware build command). All packages here are
# TypeScript-only at the source level; `.js` files in `src/` are
# always build artifacts. `tsc -b` honours `outDir` and never emits
# here. Keep these patterns as a safety net.
packages/*/src/**/*.js
packages/*/src/**/*.js.map
packages/*/src/**/*.d.ts
packages/*/src/**/*.d.ts.map

# Agent cache
.atl/.skill-registry.cache.json
.codegraph/
dist-config/
